lookbook-caption: <0>Modern day queen — ‘Winged, but rooted’</0><0>With her feet planted on the rich soil that nurtures her, she opens her arms and soars high with a head full of dreams.</0><0>Driven by her passion, she’s a city girl that reaches for the sky like a bird, yet through the seasons she stays firmly rooted in her values.</0><0>She is royalty in the way she commands and conquers, but her sophistication comes from the simplicity of just being.</0>
